text: President-elect Joe Biden receives first dose of Pfizer COVID-19 vaccine: "I’m doing this to demonstrate that people should be prepared when it’s available to take the vaccine. There’s nothing to worry about.” https://t.co/QRDIHjVJVk https://t.co/27IdGgZc66

name: ABC
text:
A woman holds her son as they watch Jupiter and Saturn, the two largest planets, align so closely that they appear as a single celestial body in the evening sky over Houston.

Astronomers call the event a “conjunction.” https://t.co/TAvpzk8kxv https://t.co/pN5umMOfWv

text: FACE-OFF: A Japanese mask store is selling hyper-realistic face masks based on people who volunteered to have their faces scanned. https://t.co/ryaPAMppIv https://t.co/XtB8pbhlxD
